name: New Gods of Raanon
blurb: Live the Legend, Be a God! In this 2D Turn Base Strategy Game players take on the role of a God leading their tribe to victory.

CELESTIAL LORD: All six New Gods of Mankind PDFs plus All three special in game units Wood Nymph Archer, Gnome Pathfinder, and Sylph Lorefinder plus 600 shekels (in game tokens) plus a trip to our studios in Las Cruces for a two day stay.
